### Role-Based Access Control Testing
### Test admin-only endpoints and role restrictions

# Variables (Update after login)
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7249@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@studentToken = YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Test Admin-Only Endpoint - Revoke User Sessions (Admin Access)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/revoke-sessions/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Test Admin-Only Endpoint - Without Admin Role (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/revoke-sessions/2
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### 3. Test Admin-Only Endpoint - Without Authentication (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/revoke-sessions/2

