### Security Test: Token Tampering
### 9. Test with Modified Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.tampered_payload.signature

### 10. Test with Different Algorithm Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwibmFtZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.